{
  "stem": "26465.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew some-- some German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the German just came towards him, and he slugged him right in the middle, in his stomach, with-- in butt of his gun.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The man crumpled on the-- on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the woman, herself, she fell to the ground, and she was just yelling and crying and bleeding all over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the two kapos came, and they grabbed her by the-- by the feet, and they dragged her away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was our first horror story that we have seen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later on, there were quite a few of those.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Year?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was '41, and we were taken-- first of all, there was the role call.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that, we were taken upstairs-- about three floors upstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was something like-- I believe it must have been either some university, or-- I have-- I don't know Krakow, at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to this day, I wouldn't know unless somebody would show me the picture of the place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were packed in there-- doesn't-- didn't matter whether there were men or women, everybody went in those small-- small probably lecture rooms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the kapos stood with their machine guns on-- on the ready, waiting, watching us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- some people-- it was first of all, I forgot to tell you, what-- and probably quite a few of the people who survived this know-- when you are so frozen and cold and it's snowing, and there is a drizzle going on, you have to go to the washroom.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no, you cannot move out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot make one step out of the quadrangle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the dogs are just standing there and waiting for you to do that-- make that move.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And where do you go?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
